OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning low cloud
OL,6,Fwill quickly burn away to leave
OL,7,Fanother dry and sunny day. The
OL,8,Fsunshine however maybe hazy at times,
OL,9,Fwith the brisk breeze continuing along
OL,10,Fthe south coast. Feeling very warm,
OL,11,Fespecially inland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining fine and dry this
OL,14,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,15,FLittle change overnight with largely
OL,16,Fclear skies, but still a notable
OL,17,Fbreeze towards the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
