OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother largely dry and
OL,6,Fsunny day across the region. A very
OL,7,Fsmall chance of the odd thunderstorm
OL,8,Fdeveloping later, mainly towards
OL,9,FCornwall. Feeling very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FRemaining largely dry and settled
OL,13,Fthroughout. A small chance of a few
OL,14,Fshowers at times, but most will avoid
OL,15,Fthem. Very warm initially but a little
OL,16,Fcooler by Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
